<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首数相同，尾数和超10的两个两位数相乘时，先求出首数与其超数之积，再加上尾数之积，最后加上尾数之和减10后与首数之积，此数即为所求之积。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">100a(a+1)+bc+(b+c-10)×10a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a表示首数，b、c分别表示被乘数与乘数个位上的数字，且b+c>10。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">68×67=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 68×67</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100×6×(6+1)+8×7+(8+7-10)×60</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4200+56+300</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=4556</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>